OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FThree police officers who were inside
OL,7,FPSNI Land rovers that came under
OL,8,Fattack during a riot in Derry which
OL,9,Fclaimed the life of Lyra McKee gave
OL,10,Fevidence at her murder trial on
OL,11,FTuesday, June 3.
OL,13,FThe 29-year old journalist and author
OL,14,Fdied after she was struck in the head
OL,15,Fby a bullet as she stood beside a
OL,16,Fpolice Landrover parked on Fanad Drive
OL,17,Fobserving the riot in the Creggan
OL,18,FEstate on the evening of April 18,
OL,19,F2019.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
