OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FThe New IRA claimed responsibility for
OL,7,Fher murder.
OL,9,FAfter a prosecuting barrister
OL,10,Fconcluded opening the Crown's case to
OL,11,FJudge Patricia Smyth at the non-jury
OL,12,Ftrial at Belfast Crown Court, three
OL,13,Fofficers who was present on the
OL,14,Fevening in question was called to give
OL,15,Fevidence.
OL,17,FThe first officer confirmed he was
OL,18,Fbehind the wheel of one of the police
OL,19,Fvehicles parked on Fanad Drive closest
OL,20,Fto the junction of Central Drive from
OL,21,Fwhere the gunman fired four shots.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
