OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FHe said he was parked in that position
OL,7,F"for a couple of hours" during which
OL,8,Fhis vehicle was attacked by "petrol
OL,9,Fbombs, stones and masonry."
OL,11,FWhen asked by a Crown barrister what
OL,12,Felse he observed, the now-retired
OL,13,Fconstable said "a couple of vehicles
OL,14,Fwere burned in the middle of the road
OL,15,Fin front of us at that stage and later
OL,16,Fon there was a gunman."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
