OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FSaying his Landrover was petrol-bombed
OL,7,F"quite repetitively", he said when the
OL,8,Fpetrol hit the windscreen and the
OL,9,Fbonnet, this produced a "large flame"
OL,10,Fand the smoke from this obscured his
OL,11,Fvision.
OL,13,FThe former officer was then asked what
OL,14,Fhappened at around 11.03pm when he
OL,15,Freceived a radio transmission and he
OL,16,Fsaid: "At the end of the wall there
OL,17,Fwas a dark figure pointing something
OL,18,Ftowards the police line, the police
OL,19,Fvehicle, and the front of our vehicle
OL,20,Fwas struck a number of times."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
