OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FHe said he then "heard a couple of
OL,7,Fpopping noises, they weren't very
OL,8,Floud, and then a couple of cracks
OL,9,Fappeared in the top right-hand side of
OL,10,Fthe windscreen belonging to the police
OL,11,Ftruck."
OL,13,FWhen he was asked by the Crown
OL,14,Fbarrister if his vehicle was still
OL,15,Fbeing petrol bombed at this stage, he
OL,16,Fanswered "yes, that was constant."
OL,18,FA second constable who on April 18,
OL,19,F2019 was with the Tactical Support
OL,20,FGroup in Strabane was also called to
OL,21,Fgive evidence.
