OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FHe was present in a police vehicle
OL,7,Fparked on Fanad Drive close to the
OL,8,Fjunction with Central Drive which he
OL,9,Fsaid came under a "sustained" attack
OL,10,Fby petrol bombs.
OL,12,FThis constable confirmed he saw a flat-
OL,13,Fbed truck being set on fire and masked
OL,14,Fmen placing a bag on the footpath at
OL,15,FFanad Drive.
OL,17,FHe was then asked if he recalled
OL,18,F"hearing the sound of gunfire" and he
OL,19,Freplied "yes I did" and said this was
OL,20,Fat around 11pm.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
