OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FWhen he was asked what he saw and
OL,7,Fheard at that point, the constable
OL,8,Fsaid: "We heard crackling then we
OL,9,Fheard a pinging noise with a small
OL,10,Fvibration off the truck.
OL,12,F"We believed at that point it may have
OL,13,Fbeen gunfire. We then looked out
OL,14,Fthrough the portholes of the truck and
OL,15,Fwe could see people frantically
OL,16,Frunning in the opposite direction."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
