OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FHe replied: "They tended to come in
OL,7,Fwaves of a group, maybe five or six
OL,8,Fmasked individuals, and several of
OL,9,Fthem would be armed with petrol bombs
OL,10,Fand they would throw them at our truck
OL,11,Fand at the truck next to us, then they
OL,12,Fwould head back towards the direction
OL,13,Fof the Creggan shops and out of view.
OL,15,F"Then every few minutes another group
OL,16,Fwould come. Same again."
OL,18,FHe was then asked by the Crown
OL,19,Fbarrister about what happened at
OL,20,Faround 11pm.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
