OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FHe answered: "My driver and the
OL,7,FInspector called out 'gunman' after I
OL,8,Fheard a popping sound. I assumed it
OL,9,Fwas more fireworks but whenever they
OL,10,Fshouted 'gunman' I assumed then there
OL,11,Fwas somebody shooting.
OL,13,F"I didn't actually see the gunman
OL,14,Fmyself, the windscreen was blacked out
OL,15,Fwith petrol bomb remnants."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
