OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FHe was then asked if he was aware of
OL,7,Fwhat happened after shots were fired
OL,8,Fand he said: "Through radio
OL,9,Ftransmissions ... I had my radio on
OL,10,Fand I could hear tranmissions that a
OL,11,Ffemale had been injured."
OL,13,FThree Derry men have been charged with
OL,14,Fmurdering Ms McKee, possessing a
OL,15,Ffirearm and ammunition and other
OL,16,Flinked offences including rioting and
OL,17,Fboth possessing and throwing petrol
OL,18,Fbombs.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
