OL,3,C'I heard popping': police describe
OL,4,Cnight of Lyra's death
OL,6,FThe trio are Paul McIntyre (56) from
OL,7,FKells Walk, 23-year old Jordan Devine
OL,8,Ffrom Bishop Street and Peter Cavanagh
OL,9,F(35) from Mary Street.
OL,11,FIt's the Crown's case that whilst none
OL,12,Fof these three defendants were the
OL,13,Fgunman who fired the fatal shot that
OL,14,Fkilled Ms Kee, their actions at the
OL,15,Fscene "are demonstrative of their
OL,16,Finvolvement in the joint enterprise to
OL,17,Fpossess and fire the weapon with the
OL,18,Frequisite intent for murder."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
