OL,6,FSeven co-accused, also from Derry, are
OL,7,Ffacing charges including rioting and
OL,8,Fthrowing petrol bombs.
OL,10,FThey are Christopher Gillen (43) from
OL,11,FBalbane Pass, Joseph Campbell (23)
OL,12,Ffrom Gosheden Gardens, 32-year old
OL,13,FPatrick Gallagher from John Field
OL,14,FPlace, Jude McCrory (26) from Gartan
OL,15,FSquare, Joseph Barr (36) from
OL,16,FSandringham Drive, 55-year old Kieran
OL,17,FMcCool from Ballymagowan Gardens and
OL,18,FWilliam Elliot (57), who is also from
OL,19,FBallymagowan Gardens.
